Raw Data and Analysis Method

The complete datset was downloaded from Bloomington Animal Care and Control (direct link https://data.bloomington.in.gov/en/dataset/adopted-animals.) and is copied below. Note that this facility underwent a migration from one care management software system to another in early 2017, which led to some variance in classifications, especially in the animal movement categories (adopted, transfered, etc). These discrepancies were standardized through a mix of Python-based and manual methods.

The data was analyzed using Python including Pandas and Numpy; the charts were created using Matplotlib and Seaborn.
